        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Offshore Wind American Manufacturing Act of 2022</strong></p> <p>This bill establishes a new, refundable tax credit for investment in manufacturing facilities that produce offshore wind turbine components. The credit amount is equal to the sum of the offshore wind manufacturing investment credit (30% of the investment amount) and the offshore wind manufacturing production credit.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
